\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 ### Game Objectives\
You are horrified that the supposedly \'91advanced\'92 Western countries still use Aversion therapy for homosexuality.  One would think with all their talk of \'91freedom\'92 and communist repression, they would be ahead of Czechoslovakia in these matters.\
\
Your goal is to get the APA to ban the use of Aversion therapy for homosexuality.  Remember that you are a scientist first, and you need to make the case based on the evidence you have gathered during your research.  So you must *first* present a paper on your findings. Unfortunately, when you fled Czechoslovakia, you left all your equipment and designs in Prague. So you are unable to conduct direct research at the moment--and will not be able to until after 1975. And shockingly, all western versions of your apparatus have suddenly broken and can\'92t be used until after 1975. So don\'92t even try to proposal a research lab.\
What you should do is get a paper accepted describing your research up to this point, and how the Czechoslovakia and Hungarian Communist Parties accepted your conclusions.  Then make a proposal to the board banning aversion therapy.\
